**PATTERNS:**
- Darkening directed at specific nations (Babylon, Egypt) ≠ literal astronomy
- Darkening = authority collapse/removal under God's judgment  
- Physical signs may accompany but prophetic vocabulary chosen because sun/moon/stars = rulers
- Babylon burns → smoke rises → sun black-as-sackcloth → Christ appears in clouds/smoke
- Sequence: tribulation → authority structure collapses → new supreme authority (Christ) appears
- Not cosmic destruction - regime change on cosmic scale